==Prove of the Offence==
# [[Canadian Criminal Law/Identity|identity]] of accused
# [[Canadian Criminal Law/Jurisdiction and Time|date and time]] of incident
# [[Canadian Criminal Law/Jurisdiction and Time|jurisdiction]] (incl. region and province)
# the accused disobeyed a lawful order of the Court;
# the accused was without a lawful excuse;
# the accused intended to disobey the order of the Court; and
# what the order required the accused to do.<Ref>R v Solar, 2012 SKQB 113 at 32</ref>

