* {{tl|Ntsh}} â€“ same as this template, but does not display (hides) the number
* {{tl|Ntsc}} â€“ for converted units, sorts by the first number
* {{tl|Ntss}} â€“ same as Nts, but allows for the number to be scaled
* {{tl|Convert}} â€“ has a sortable option
* {{tl|Dts}} â€“ for sorting dates
* {{tl|Sms}} â€“ used to generate <u>any</u> hidden sort key
<includeonly>
[[Category:Sorting templates|Nts]]
</includeonly>

